---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="EXPRESS BOOKS™ — Fast Reads. Lasting Impact."
	description="Spirit Media's signature publishing format — intentionally compact books designed to be read in a single sitting."
>
	<main id="main-content">

		<!-- HERO -->
		<section class="bg-white px-6 py-20 lg:py-28 lg:px-8 overflow-hidden">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
					<div class="hero-stagger">
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-4">EXPRESS BOOKS™</p>
						<h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-gray-900">Fast reads.<br /><span class="text-red-600">Lasting impact.</span></h1>
						<p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600 max-w-xl">Not every message needs 300 pages. Some of the most powerful truths can be shared in under an hour.</p>
						<div class="mt-8">
							<a href="/contact" class="rounded-md bg-red-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-red-700">Request a Call →</a>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="hidden lg:grid grid-cols-3 gap-3" aria-hidden="true" data-animate="zoom-in">
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-600 aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-800 aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-600 aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-900 aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-700 aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-800 aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-600 aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-900 aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-800 aspect-square"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ABOUT -->
		<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-3" data-animate="fade-up">The Format</p>
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">Publishing Designed for Multiplication</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">EXPRESS BOOKS™ is Spirit Media's signature publishing format — intentionally compact books designed to be read in a single sitting. No filler. No fluff. Just your message, distilled to its most potent form. Transformation that lasts a lifetime.</p>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="3">At roughly 80 pages, every EXPRESS BOOK™ is affordably priced for easy sharing — hand one to a friend, leave one in a waiting room, ship a box to a pastor overseas. This is publishing designed for multiplication.</p>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="4">Every EXPRESS BOOK™ is published in three formats: paperback, eBook, and downloadable PDF — with global distribution through Amazon, IngramSpark, and eBook stores worldwide.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- FORMATS -->
		<section class="bg-white py-20 px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
					<div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 text-center" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">
						<div class="flex h-14 w-14 mx-auto items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-600 mb-4">
							<svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 0 0 6 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0 1 6 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 0 1 6-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0 0 18 18a8.967 8.967 0 0 0-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25" /></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Paperback</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Roughly 80 pages, affordably priced for easy sharing and multiplication.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 text-center" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">
						<div class="flex h-14 w-14 mx-auto items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-600 mb-4">
							<svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 1.5H8.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 6 3.75v16.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25h7.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 18 20.25V3.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25H13.5m-3 0V3h3V1.5m-3 0h3m-6 18.75h6" /></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">eBook</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Digital distribution to 1 billion eBook users worldwide.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 text-center" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="3">
						<div class="flex h-14 w-14 mx-auto items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-600 mb-4">
							<svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 13.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375H8.25m2.25 0H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 0 0-9-9Z" /></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Downloadable PDF</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Accessible anywhere, on any device. Perfect for global distribution.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- CTA -->
		<section class="bg-red-600 px-6 py-20 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-white sm:text-4xl mb-4" data-animate="fade-up">Ready to publish your EXPRESS BOOK™?</h2>
				<p class="text-red-100 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">Your message doesn't need 300 pages. Let us help you distill it to its most powerful form.</p>
				<a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 font-semibold px-8 py-3.5 rounded-md hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">Request a Call →</a>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>
</Layout>
